Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,起床 起床 起床
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,起床 这群垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,床
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧换装到海岸集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起来 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,追加来回海岸五趟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 接下来开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的E级队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,全员睁眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,书面学习也是重要的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的学餐真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,美味…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,饿着肚子可打不了仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗? 吃得下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一点点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好吃饭可撑不过下午的训练呦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时一直都在睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是石动北杜 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,顶带一提是D级的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,D级…倒数第二呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是最后一名就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们处境差不多 就好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,里面那位也请多指教啰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们为什么一直在睡觉啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,睡眠不足? 晚上没睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上还是有好好睡觉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上都被魔鬼教官的训练给累个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好 早练就到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,上完课再回来这边继续跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,做好觉悟呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,E级还有教官跟着啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,D级没有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A级到D级都由同一个人负责呦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叫做珀拉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样的人? 恶鬼? 恶魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不对 是个温柔的人呦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要准备下午的课了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是个开朗的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然只有小生们的教官比较特别呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要从那个教官的掌心逃离的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一级也好 必须要升级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不舒服的话下午的课就休息吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过绝对不要勉强自己呦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有逃跑乖乖回来了呢 值得褒扬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好想逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,开始特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起来跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只有跑步吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太不合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是跑步的话可发泄不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想要战斗呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想打的话等等就让你打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,追加来回10趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各务原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 回答啊 各务原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙 振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候倒下了…然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你一直都在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且把你带去保健室了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但原因说是积劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只要好好睡一觉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有消除疲劳了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,精神有比较好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是马铃薯炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐是谁负责的来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这道马铃薯炖肉是教官做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那个恶鬼做的马铃薯炖肉…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她不生气的时候意外的很温柔呦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要生气保持温柔就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有股怀念的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙 不要太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不想扯大家的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 莉洁儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都很关心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我是你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但主要任务还是监视你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是在保障你的安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这些我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎从一开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,两人关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿阁下真的很关心安昙阁下的身体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有点意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要一起吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,让我参一脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小生也同席
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这个马铃薯炖肉真的很好吃对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待下午的训练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不想干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙 还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,教官不在?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 说不定下午没有训练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也要训练呦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午的训练跟以往不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是…战场生成装置?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,场地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,生成装置?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边有着巨大的椿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,露营我可拿手了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 用这应该能撑起挺大的帐篷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是要前往战斗训练用空间的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我也是第一次看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Z/X还在侵略时做的初期机型呦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,学校已经视为古董退下一线了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但还能用我就拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪这么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,反正能用就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好像 有点有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的像是来露营的老爹呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呆看啥啊这群垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人一起推呐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不想再做事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺棘手的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好 差不多就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,生成战场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是战场?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去啰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,银河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从战场内看不到外面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了让人能集中于战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 从外面可以看到里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 这个战场的特征就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击停下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,出现护罩了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是实战模拟反冲击限制模式2号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,通称模拟战模式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好 都明白了就先出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没能反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个场地内的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不会直接对身体造成伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,会有些许冲击穿过护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有时也可能会淤青
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,准备了这东西也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要用Z/X进行1对1实战训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了掌握各自的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,借此进行有效的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,达至更高效的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好 想战斗的人举手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我 交给小生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 鬼神野朱里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里好勤奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好 各务原安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太勉强了 安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天才累倒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我来保护你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚也说明过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,战场内的攻击不会直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就尽情打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…之前就一直很好奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里的Z/X在哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是把刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是把刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等盟友 绝刀职人村正呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,两边都准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙 躲到我身后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道安昙这么努力的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,新生训练时的战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不能撇开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙可能会因此觉得自己是个拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙长时间待在医疗舱中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,最近才出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要强求战斗素养才是强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,以Z/X没实体化的人类做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一瞬间就解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神野流秘剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,远雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神野流秘剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,水镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,退到后面 安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,正正当当 正是吾愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,朱里的近距离影斗力高的异常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙连自己的战斗距离都不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿应该是更灵活 更稳重的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就再接近一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神野流拔刀术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿 拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,暗光也被
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,情势改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,自己在战场上的站位意外的难抓呦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其对纯战斗型的战斗服来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那场训练战中 她畏缩也是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定是我们全员的站位太差了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个距离下 就能看清对手的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,从弹幕之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 打扰到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,双方到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,以垃圾来说做的很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莉洁儿 好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,明明应该是小生赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这场胜负平手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好 下一埸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不间断打下去呦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小生还能打呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,继续特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,光看就累了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,被保护的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 安昙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————OP———————————
